Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.94,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,僕と君は別々だから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:29.53,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,当たり前のもっと前から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.49,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,話をしようか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.66,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,伝達された花の名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.33,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,知らなくとも綺麗と言えること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.79,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,頬に触れた暖かさを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.34,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,優しさだと呼び合えること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:50.01,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,君は僕の、僕は君の、そばにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.93,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,君を分かりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.22,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,そのための涙さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:04.90,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,情けない僕だけど迎えに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.28,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,言いたいのはただ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.61,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,悲しみも大嫌いも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:17.49,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,さよならも君がいるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.79,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:26.67,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:11.64,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,想要了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.94,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我們終究有別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:29.53,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,所以在彼此交錯前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.49,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,互相傾訴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.66,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,君傳頌之花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.33,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,不曉其名也能欣賞它的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.79,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,觸碰你臉頰時的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.34,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,一定就是所謂的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:50.01,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,你與我 我與你 相互依偎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.93,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,想要了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.22,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,即使淚如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:04.90,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,軟弱的我仍義無反顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.28,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我想說的僅是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.61,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我能夠跨越悲傷 厭惡與離別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:17.49,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,皆只因有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.79,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:26.67,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,矢志不渝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:38.87,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}空の彼方約束を果たせるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:46.50,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}私はあなたと共に在りたいと願う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.61,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:53.31,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正しいとかそうじゃないとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.66,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}自分次第だよって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:03.53,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}頭で分かってるつもり心は連れない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.42,0:23:10.44,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時として言葉は心を現わすには不十分だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.50,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}しょうがないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:15.96,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}弱い自分裏返す強い自分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:21.51,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}あなたに相応しい私でいられるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:25.99,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:27.99,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}失くせないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.48,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}諦められないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:34.35,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Keeping promises
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.98,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}誓うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.32,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}辿る空で待っていると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.52,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:41.74,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:44.68,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}自分の心に届いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:45.68,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:48.77,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}残された二日を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:49.92,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.65,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}決意は揺るがない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:53.78,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.50,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}もう一人の自分にグッバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.23,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:38.87,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}去實現於天空彼方的約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:46.50,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈願與你並肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.61,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:53.31,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正確與否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.66,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:03.53,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.42,0:23:10.44,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而詞不達意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.50,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}這也無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:15.96,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}讓弱小的我變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:21.51,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是為與你相稱
Comment: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:25.99,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:27.99,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.48,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如無法放棄
Comment: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:34.35,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Keeping promises
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.98,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}既然立下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.32,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我將在彼方守候
Comment: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.52,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
Comment: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:41.74,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:44.68,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直達內心
Comment: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:45.68,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:48.77,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}擁抱僅剩的兩日
Comment: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:49.92,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.65,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我的決心矢志不渝
